flowchart LR
    A[Customer Query] --> B[Load SQLite Memory]
    B --> C[Classify Intent]
    C -->|Memory recall| M[Memory Agent]
    C -->|Sales / Technical / Billing / Account| R[Retrieve Knowledge Base Context]
    R --> D{Route by Department}
    D -->|Sales| S[Sales Support Agent]
    D -->|Technical| T[Technical Support Agent]
    D -->|Billing| G[Billing Support Agent]
    D -->|Account| Q[Account Support Agent]
    S --> H{High-Risk Request?}
    T --> H
    G --> H
    Q --> H
    H -->|Yes| P[Human Supervisor Approval]
    H -->|No| V[Supervisor Validation]
    P --> V
    M --> W[Save Conversation Memory]
    V --> W
    W --> Z[Final Customer Response]
